// vercel.json.patch
// MERGE INSTRUCTION:
// If your engine uses pages/api/ or app/api/ routing in Next.js,
// the api/ directory files in this patch zip are auto-routed by Vercel —
// no vercel.json change needed.
//
// If the engine has a vercel.json with explicit "functions" or "rewrites"
// blocks, ensure these two endpoints are reachable:
//
//   POST /api/github_webhook
//   POST /api/vercel_webhook
//
// Both must:
//   - accept POST only
//   - have raw body access for HMAC signature verification
//   - return 200 fast (< 5s) — webhook providers retry on timeout
//
// REQUIRED ENV VARS in Vercel for pranix-agent-engine:
//   GITHUB_WEBHOOK_SECRET   (generate: openssl rand -hex 32)
//   VERCEL_WEBHOOK_SECRET   (generate: openssl rand -hex 32)
//
// (Plus the already-present: SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY,
//  GITHUB_PAT, GITHUB_SECONDARY_PAT, VERCEL_TOKEN, VERCEL_SECONDARY_TOKEN)
